<div class="title">Permanent Smile on My Face</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Dexedrine)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Cya&Exact=1">Cya</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Cya. "Permanent Smile on My Face: An Experience with Amphetamines (Dexedrine) (exp34704)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 21, 2013. erowid.org/exp/34704</div>

<br/>



